These are Puzzles for 5x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-8-1::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, quad-bike
2 different games are played: monopoly, canasta
House: cottage, farmhouse
There are 2 different nationalities: nigerian, spanish
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: classical, soul
1. the fan of classical is on the far right##1
2. the farmhouse house is on the left or right of the spanish##3
3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the person driving the motorbike##3
4. the fan of soul is not to the right of the fan of classical##8
5. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
6. the person playing monopoly is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2       |
| Transport    | quad-bike   | motorbike        |
| Game   | monopoly    | canasta |
| House     | farmhouse  | cottage       |
| Nationality     | nigerian   | spanish         |
| Music-Genre   | soul | classical      |

