.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-8-2::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: azalea, zinnia
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, old-henry
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, jet-ski
There are 2 different favourite colors: white, blood-red
2 different games are played: monopoly, scrabble
1. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the jet-ski is not to the right of the person who likes blood-red##8
4. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| Flower         | azalea   | zinnia |
| Cigar   | old-henry  | bolivar     |
| Transport   | bike  | jet-ski        |
| Color           | white     | blood-red       |
| Game         | monopoly | scrabble     |

